%% Diagram: CompositorFrameSink BeginFrame ↔ SubmitFrame loop
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Display as Display (VSync)
    participant Viz as Viz (Display Compositor)
    participant Sink as CompositorFrameSink
    participant CC as Compositor Thread
    participant Main as Main Thread

    Display->>Viz: VSync tick
    Viz->>Sink: BeginFrame(args)
    Sink->>CC: BeginImplFrame
    CC->>Main: BeginMainFrame (if needed)
    Main-->>CC: ReadyToCommit + Commit
    CC->>CC: Activate (NOW tiles ready)
    CC->>CC: Build CompositorFrame
    CC->>Sink: SubmitCompositorFrame(frame)
    Sink->>Viz: SubmitCompositorFrame
    Viz->>Viz: SurfaceAggregator merges all surfaces
    Viz->>Display: GPU draw + present
    Viz-->>Sink: DidReceiveCompositorFrameAck
    Sink-->>CC: Recycle resources
